divs: Sighting DetailsBright white, Diamond shaped object, larger, and brighter than Venus, observed in early morning sky, through windshield, while driving south on I-355, from Rt.64, at the time, it did not seem to be moving, but stayed somewhat stationary. Approached I-55 Exit, & lost sight of Object. Always drive this same route to work, never seen this type of object before !
Summary: Bright white Diamond shaped object observe in early morning sky
